Attributes.description: Orientation to psychological research, with special emphasis on ongoing research within the department; effective presentation of research findings, oral and written; critical evaluation of research. Requires a research project.
Attributes.prereq: Pre-reqs: Either (a) PSYC 100 or (b) all of PSYC 101, PSYC 102; and all of PSYC 217, 218. (Restricted to students in Honours.)
